      {
        "id": "arcane_shield",
        "name": "Arcane Shield",
        "text": "(Psychic) (PSYKER only): While this model is leading a unit, models in that unit have a 4+ invulnerable save.",
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Psyker"
          }
        ],
        "points": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "binding_tendrils",
        "name": "Binding Tendrils",
        "text": "(Psychic) (PSYKER only): In your Shooting phase, after this model has shot, select one enemy Infantry unit hit by one or more of those attacks made with a Psychic weapon. Until the start of your next turn, that unit is ensnared. While a unit is ensnared, subtract 2\" from its Move characteristic and subtract 2 from Charge rolls made for it.",
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Psyker"
          }
        ],
        "points": 0
      },
      {
        "id": "empyric_guidance",
        "name": "Empyric Guidance",
        "text": "(Psychic) (PSYKER only): Weapons equipped by models in this unit have the [LETHAL HITS] ability.",
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Psyker"
          }
        ],
        "points": 0
      },
      {
        "id": "malefic_will",
        "name": "Malefic Will",
        "text": "Weapons equipped by models in this unit have the [SUSTAINED HITS 1] ability.",
        "points": 0
      },
      {
        "id": "marked_by_fate",
        "name": "Marked by Fate",
        "text": "(Psychic) (PSYKER only): In your Shooting phase, after this model's unit has shot, select one enemy unit hit by one or more of those attacks made with a Psychic weapon. Until the end of the phase, each time a friendly THOUSAND SONS unit makes an attack that targets that enemy unit, add 1 to the Hit roll.",
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Psyker"
          }
        ],
        "points": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "swathed_in_illusion",
        "name": "Swathed in Illusion",
        "text": "This unit can only be selected as the target of a ranged attack if the attacking model is within 18\".",
        "points": 0
      },
      {
        "id": "twisted_sorceries",
        "name": "Twisted Sorceries",
        "text": "(Psychic) (PSYKER only): Once per battle, in your Shooting phase or the Fight phase, this model can use this ability. If it does, until the end of the phase, improve the Strength and Attacks characteristics of Psychic weapons equipped by this model by 1.",
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Psyker"
